# Iron John (Σιδηρόγιαννος, Θανάσης Χρυσός 2018, Greek) — derived entirely from the
# game source: NO published walkthrough exists (corpus.tsv wt="-"). Interactive
# retelling of the Grimm tale in 5 playable chapters (ch3/ch6 are wait-driven
# cutscenes the harness auto-continues). MAX SCORE 35/35 (all 20 scoreup events),
# ends at the genuine finish (kef6, "ΤΕΛΟΣ"). Timing constraints honoured:
#  - reach the throne room within 7 turns of game start (settask gate, +1);
#  - follow the dog scent trail d1-s-s-e-n-e landing on d7limni at EXACTLY
#    dog.startsmell+5 (firstenter equality check, +2);
#  - hand the σημείωμα to the gardener at once (kipouros_script evicts you
#    after 2 turns in the hut);
#  - give the ΑΓΡΙΟΛΟΥΛΟΥΔΑ (livadi wildflowers, 9-turn wilt timer) to the
#    princess — the bostani garden flowers are the unscored decoy path.
